# Apex by Chargebee Design System

## Brand Colors

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `brand-navy` | `#1c1b2e` | Primary text, icons, headers |
| `brand-deep` | `#13121f` | Dark backgrounds |
| `brand-soft` | `#2e2c4a` | Secondary dark surfaces |
| `brand-mist` | `#9b99b4` | Muted text |
| `brand-fog` | `#6b6885` | Placeholder text |

## Accent Colors

### Orange (Primary Actions, CTAs)
- `orange-500`: `#ff3300` - Primary buttons, active states
- `orange-100`: `#ffe5de` - Active nav item backgrounds
- `orange-50`: `#fff5f2` - Subtle hover backgrounds

### Violet (AI Surfaces)
- `violet-500`: `#6d28d9` - AI-related elements
- `violet-50`: `#f5f3ff` - AI surface backgrounds

### AI Gradient
- Direction: Top to bottom (`#ff3300` → `#8b5cf6`)
- Use for AI-centric icons and elements
- Animate with 3s pulse for "ephemeral" feel

## Typography

| Purpose | Font | Weights |
|---------|------|---------|
| Body text | Inter | 400, 500, 600 |
| Headings | Sora | 400, 500, 600, 700 |

## Corner Radius

- **Default**: Use `rounded-full` for badges, tags, pills
- **Buttons/Cards**: Use `rounded-lg` (8px)
- **Small elements**: Use `rounded-md` (6px)
- **Exception**: Only use smaller radius when explicitly specified

## Layout Structure

### Left Navigation
- Width: `w-12` (48px)
- Position: Fixed, full height
- Padding: `pt-2 pb-3`
- Icon size: 18px
- Active state: `bg-orange-100 text-orange-500` with `h-7 w-7`

### Top Navigation
- Height: `h-10` (40px)
- Position: Fixed, offset by left nav (`left-12`)
- Z-index: `z-30` (below left nav's `z-40`)

## Icon Guidelines

- Library: Lucide React
- Default size: 18px for nav, 16px for actions, 14px for inline
- AI icons: Use animated gradient stroke (see GradientMessageSquarePlus pattern)

## Semantic Colors

| State | Background | Text |
|-------|------------|------|
| Success | `green-50` | `green-700` |
| Warning | `amber-50` | `amber-700` |
| Danger | `red-50` | `red-700` |
| Info | `blue-50` | `blue-700` |
| Live | `green-50` with `green-500` dot | `green-700` |

## Interactive States

```tsx
// Hover states for buttons/clickable elements
className="transition-colors hover:bg-neutral-100"

// Active nav item
className="bg-orange-100 text-orange-500"
```

## Workbench Page Patterns

### Header Layout
- Title: `text-[20px] font-semibold text-brand-navy` with `letter-spacing: -0.5px`
- Title positioned left with `left-6 bottom-2.5`
- Tabs absolutely centered on screen with `left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2`
- Horizontal line spans from `left-6` to `right-4` (aligns with title and avatar)
- Header height: 72px expanded, 56px compact (on scroll)

### Content Area
- Max width: `max-w-[1560px]` centered with `mx-auto`
- Background: Pure white (`bg-white`)
- Padding: `px-6 py-8`

### Stats Section
- Spread across width using `flex flex-1`
- Vertical line separators: `h-12 w-px bg-neutral-200`
- Value: `text-[32px] font-semibold text-brand-navy`
- Label: `text-[13px] text-brand-fog`

### Data Tables
- Use native `<table>` with `overflow-x-auto` for horizontal scroll
- Header: `text-[11px] font-normal uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-fog`
- Body text: `text-[14px] text-brand-navy`
- Row hover: `hover:bg-neutral-50`
- Borders: `border-b border-neutral-100` for rows

### Filter/Sort Tags (Notion-style)
- Height: `h-6` (24px)
- Border radius: `rounded-full`
- Font: `text-[13px]`
- Style: `border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:bg-neutral-50`
- Labels: `text-brand-fog` for prefix, `font-medium` for value

### Severity Tags
| Level | Background | Text |
|-------|------------|------|
| Critical | `bg-red-50` | `text-red-600` |
| High | `bg-amber-50` | `text-amber-600` |
| Medium | `bg-yellow-50` | `text-yellow-600` |
| Low | `bg-green-50` | `text-green-600` |

### Task Type Tags
- Neutral styling for all: `bg-neutral-100 text-brand-navy border-neutral-200`
- Compact: `px-2 py-0.5 text-[12px] rounded-full`

## Full-Page Modal Patterns

### Modal Shell
- Outer padding: `p-4` (16px on all sides)
- Corner radius: `rounded-[24px]`
- Overlay: `bg-black/40`
- Z-index: `z-50`
- Body scroll lock when open

### Modal Top Bar
- Padding: `px-6 py-4`
- Border: `border-b border-neutral-200`
- Close button: `h-8 w-8` icon button, left-aligned
- Title: `font-heading text-[18px] font-semibold text-brand-navy`
- Primary CTA: `bg-violet-500`, Sora font, semibold, `rounded-lg`, trailing arrow icon

### Modal Body
- Two-column layout: `grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 p-4`
- Left column: Contract preview (fixed height, scrollable if needed)
- Right column: Interaction area (`overflow-y-auto`)

### AI-Powered Interactions
- Match count header: AI gradient icon + `ai-gradient-text`
- Closest match badge: Full `ai-gradient` background, white text
- Regular match badge: `bg-violet-100 text-violet-700`
- Selected state: `bg-violet-50` row highlight

### Form Fields (Inline Edit Style)
- Label: `text-[13px] text-brand-fog`
- Value display: `border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg px-3 py-2`
- Edit mode: `bg-neutral-100` (light grey), autofocused
- Section cards: `rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-5`
